  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are looking for a dedicated and organised Sales Executive to join our growing digital lock business. The ideal candidate will play a pivotal role in providing excellent customer service and ensuring smooth day-to-day operations.<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist walk-in customers with inquiries, providing product information and support.</li><li>Respond promptly and professionally to customer requests via WhatsApp Business and other communication channels.</li><li>Manage general administrative tasks, including maintaining records, processing orders, and coordinating schedules.</li><li>Support the team in handling operational activities, such as inventory checks and basic reporting.</li><li>Address and escalate customer concerns to the relevant team members when necessary.</li><li>Perform ad-hoc duties as required to support the business.</li></ul><h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3><p><strong>Qualifications & Experience:</strong></p><ul><li>Singaporean/PR</li><li>Prior experience in customer service or sales roles is a plus.</li></ul><p><strong>Skills & Competencies:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong communication skills, both verbal and written.</li><li>Proficient in Google Drive and comfortable with using WhatsApp Business.</li><li>Highly organised and detail-oriented with the ability to multitask.</li><li>Customer-focused with a friendly and professional demeanour.</li><li>Able to work independently and as part of a team.</li></ul><p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p><ul><li>Work location: 501 Jurong West Street 51, Singapore 640501</li><li>Work hours: 9.30 am - 6 pm</li><li>Attractive remuneration package with opportunities for growth.</li></ul>",
